{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643810/extras/DiscordButton.png?t=1734561624\" /><br><br><strong>Betrayal Beach</strong> is an online social deduction survival game for 4-8 players. Crash landed on a strange island, a group of survivors must work together to survive long enough for rescue to come. However, 1-2 players are working as saboteurs. Blending in with the survivors of the crash, their goal is to make sure none leave the island alive.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643810/extras/Banner_Survivors.png?t=1734561624\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Collect</strong> resource cards to contribute to objectives or keep yourself alive.<br></li><li> <strong>Craft</strong> useful gear, such as spears to fend off animal attacks or a basket to carry more resources.<br></li><li> <strong>Manage</strong> your health, hunger, and limited inventory space.<br></li><li> <strong>Deliberate</strong> with fellow survivors and vote to exile the saboteur from camp.<br></li><li> <strong>Play</strong> as 3 unique roles with extra abilities.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643810/extras/Banner_Saboteurs.png?t=1734561624\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Blend in</strong> with the survivors to gain their trust.<br></li><li> <strong>Sabotage</strong> objectives to stall the survivors' progress and put them in danger.<br></li><li> <strong>Unleash Suffering</strong> by activating strange totems and opening mysterious caches.<br></li><li> <strong>Lie</strong>, deceive, betray, and sow chaos!<br></li><li> <strong>Play</strong> as 2 unique roles with extra abilities.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2643810/extras/Banner_Features.png?t=1734561624\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><l